# Delete Your Account and Data

## How to Delete Your Account

To delete your account and associated data, please follow these steps:

1. Open the app and navigate to the **Account** screen.
2. Tap on the **Delete Account** button.
3. Confirm your choice by following the prompts provided.

Your account and all associated data will be permanently deleted. Please note that some data may be retained for a limited time as required by law or for security purposes.

---

## Additional Information

If you encounter any issues or have further questions about deleting your account, please contact our support team at [support@example.com].
